{"tid":1772360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】17次去信索開槍警資料不獲受理 右眼中彈印尼女記者入稟要求警交代身份","createTime":"2019-12-06T14:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T17:04:57.000Z","uid":47496,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b5af2b7d8f6dcf9eda3b309017b4fe26660437ad","tid":1772360,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"【抗暴之戰】17次去信索開槍警資料不獲受理 右眼中彈印尼女記者入稟要求警交代身份<br />\n<br />\n39歲印尼女記者維比（Veby Mega Indah）於9月29日在灣仔採訪期間，疑遭警員以橡膠子彈射傷右眼，視力永久受損。她擬提出民事訴訟，惟早前向警方索取涉事警員資料不果。她今入稟高等法院，申請訴訟前的文件披露，要求警務處處長向她的代表律師提供展示開槍警員身份的文件。案件將於明年1月3日聆訊，預計約需半小時。<br />\n<br />\n維比的代表律師韋智達（Michael Vidler）表示，維比認為事件已超過兩個月，其間曾17次去信要求警務處公開涉事警員身份，惟一直被拒，遂決定放棄向警方提出要求，直接向高院入稟。韋智達表示，由於維比等候警方已逾兩個月，仍未有任何回應，而提出私人檢控的限期為六個月；加上現在只能假設警方並非調查中，同時亦無信心警方會主動調查案件，遂入稟高院，以便在限期內提出私人檢控。<br />\n<br />\n維比索取9月29日下午約4時50分在灣仔入境事務大樓天橋通往告士打道的樓梯上，開槍傷及她的警員的資料。入稟狀要求警方交出由9月28日至今，警方保管的所有顯示到該警員身份和警員編號的文件，包括供詞、報告、通訊和電腦紀錄等。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCMP2249/19】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191206&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60350427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191206%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60350427&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqrudDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=4d839a30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191206%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60350427&h=6e9ab167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191206&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60350427</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df305a06847e03c8ce3e8873731adbed927e35d","tid":1772360,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:17:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c657abb57133d1425cf35f944d27e4e9f939dae3","tid":1772360,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec8bae7972b39c91faea4afec6f730c7841e27a","tid":1772360,"uid":131323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:27:17.000Z","msg":"警務處:又唔係美國記者 印尼就算9數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2528e4c3a7fb81f76cdb634ba7f3cf8cb4e48b","tid":1772360,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"印尼奶共，沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efcfe53db1c59ec0ddefbe611cc37eef9d0b6bb","tid":1772360,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:29:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3c0339bfa70d52bd3d2d51b80ddb986cc9d19e","tid":1772360,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76566c16bd14bbc47781eee804071105058c54b4","tid":1772360,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972d196d76076ffe93632b2eec758fb0b4dd8fd8","tid":1772360,"uid":137483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:35:13.000Z","msg":"有無可能泛民提出私人草案廢除功能組別, 然後反對嘅人就交俾美國制裁?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1772330\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1772330</a>"},{"pid":"07c1c62e1b01eb428285e4a02832bda2fe220845","tid":1772360,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:36:15.000Z","msg":"<strong>而提出私人檢控的限期為六個月</strong><br />\n唔怪之得要拖"},{"pid":"e2b5fed4f10d0ca0ab3b1bb1b1367fbb85ad5331","tid":1772360,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12